description: Datz It Datz All is serving San Antonio a taste of Texas with a delicious touch of Louisiana Creole-Soul. Their savory selection of Po’Boys, Gumbo, Fried Catfish, Shrimp Tacos, (and much more!) are all packed with amazingly authentic flavors, you're sure to love every bite.Dash your way straight to Datz It Datz All for authentic dishes that are really quite incredible.
name: Datz It Datz All
